languages.text: "Выживший повстанец рассказал о странных экспериментах, которые проводят над населением Януса. Говорят, людей свозят в поместье и больше их никто не видел. Знаешь что-то про это?"

"The rebel that survived talked about strange experiments being conducted on the people of Janus. It is said that people are brought to the estate and never seen again. Do you know anything about that?"

languages.text: “那些幸存下来的叛军士兵说，有人在加努斯进行古怪的人体实验。据说那些人被带到了庄园之后，就再也没人见过他们。你知道这件事情吗？”

languages.text: «El rebelde que sobrevivió habló de experimentos extraños con la gente de Janus. Se rumorea que llevan personas a la mansión y nunca se vuelve a saber de ellas. ¿Tienes alguna información al respecto?».

languages.text: 「反乱兵の生き残りが、ヤヌスの住民に行われていた妙な実験について話していた。住民は屋敷に連れて行かれたきり、二度と姿を見せないそうだ。この件について何か知っていることはないか？」
languages.original_text: "The rebel that survived talked about strange experiments being conducted on the people of Janus. It is said that people are brought to the estate and never seen again. Do you know anything about that?"

languages.text: "Der überlebende Rebell hat von seltsamen Experimenten am Volk von Janus gesprochen. Es heißt, Leute würden zum Anwesen gebracht und dann nie mehr gesehen. Wisst Ihr etwas darüber?"
languages.original_text: "The rebel that survived talked about strange experiments being conducted on the people of Janus. It is said that people are brought to the estate and never seen again. Do you know anything about that?"

languages.text: « Le rebelle survivant a parlé d'étranges expériences menées sur les habitants de Janus. À ses dires, les ouvriers sont parfois conduits au domaine de la gouverneure et ne réapparaissent jamais. Êtes-vous au courant de quoi que ce soit à ce sujet ? »

languages.text: "Sağ kalan isyancı, Janus halkı üzerinde tuhaf deneyler yapıldığından söz etmişti. İnsanların konağa götürülüyor ve bir daha görülmüyorlarmış. Bu konuda bir şey biliyor musun?"
